43. 'operational states' state starting.
44. Transition 'starting-running': from starting, accepts 'Vehicle On Signal', then running.
45. 'operational states' state running.
46. 'running' entry: 'perform self check'.
47. 'running' do: 'provide power'.
48. 'running' exit: 'apply parking brake'.
49. Transition 'running-off': from running, accepts 'Vehicle Off Signal', does 'notify controller off' with in controller = vehicleA_c1.vehicleController, then off.

50. Defines substate 'health states'.
51. 'health states' entry action initial.
52. 'health states' transition initial then normal.
53. 'health states' state normal.
54. Transition 'normal-maintenance': from normal, accepts 'Maintenance Signal', then maintenance.
55. Transition 'normal-degraded': from normal, accepts when 'sense temperature'.temperature > vehicleA_c1.Tmax, does 'notify controller over temperature' with in controller = vehicleA_c1.vehicleController, then degraded.
56. 'health states' state maintenance.
57. Transition 'maintenance-normal': from maintenance, accepts 'Restore to Normal', then normal.
58. 'health states' state degraded.
59. Transition 'degraded-normal': from degraded, accepts 'Restore to Normal', then normal.
60. 'health states' do: 'sense temperature' { out temperature; }

#### State Machine: 'controller states'
61. Defines state 'controller states' as 'Controller States'.
62. 'controller states' entry action initial.
63. 'controller states' transition initial then off.
64. 'controller states' state off.
65. Transition 'off-on': from off, accepts 'Start Signal', then on.
66. 'controller states' state on.
67. Transition 'on-off': from on, accepts 'Off Signal', then off.

#### Part Instance: vehicleA_c1
68. Defines part vehicleA_c1 of type VehicleA.
69. vehicleA_c1 has attribute 'brake pedal pressed' of type Boolean.
70. vehicleA_c1 has attribute Tmax of type TemperatureValue.
71. vehicleA_c1 has part vehicleController of type VehicleController.
72. vehicleController exhibits 'controller states' as VehicleController::'controller states'.
73. vehicleA_c1 exhibits 'vehicle states' as VehicleA::'vehicle states'.
